player createDiaryRecord ["Diary", ["Informacio","
	-------------------
	<br />
	-- Parametres --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	Pots canviar la teva disntancia de visio al menu d'accio. Tambe pots crear grups separats a través de l'opcio de Parametres al menu d'accio.
	<br />
	-------------------  
	<br />
	-- Suport --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	SL, JTAC and UAV Operators can call for support from the 0-8 Menu. AH-99 and A-164 Air support will loiter around until fuel is low or out of ammo or 30 minutes on station then RTB for resupply. This will take at least 30 minutes. UAV support starts at base and will fly from base towards the position on map where you selected so take control of it sometime after you call it in and give it some kind of waypoint or you might lose the UAV. UGV parachutes in and moves to position selected on map. AR-2 Darter can be called by the Team Leaders and UAV Operators. AR-2 Darter, UAV and UGV will automatically connect to you if you have the uav terminal when they are called in. Only the Squad Leader can call in an Ammo Crate air drop.
	<br />
	-------------------  
	<br />
	-- Vehicles --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	Tots els vehicles reapareixen despres de 5 minuts si ja no es poden moure i ningu esta a l'interior o son destruits. Els vehicles operatius requereixen que els jugadors estiguin mes enlla de 300 metres per tal que reapareguin. Pot crear vehicles terrestres, aeronaus i embarcacions en les senyals marcades al mapa. Els vehicles generats pel jugador no reapareixen i son seguits a nivell local. Nomes pots tenir 2 vehicles en qualsevol moment. Si tens vehicles destruits o que no es poden moure, seran eliminats una vegada que obris el quadre de dialeg de creacio de vehicles. Els vehicles tenen capacitat de carrega i poden carregar altres vehicles o caixes de municio, segons la mida. Si un vehicle esta en una zona de creacio de vehicles i ningu esta a l'interior, s'eliminara sense importar qui el va generar.
	<br />
	-------------------  
	<br />
	-- Slingload --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	The UH-80 and CH-49 can slingload various vehicles based on Raven's Lifter mod if used. If not then heavy and medium helicopters can slingload ATVs, Boats, Car type vehicles, Static Weapons via action menu if you are the pilot. Only heavy helicopters can slingload heavy Car Types and Armor Types while medium helicopters is limited to lighter Car Types. Light helicopters can only sling static weapons and ammo boxes. To slingload you need to be over the object and fly between 10-16 altitude and be going less than 40 kph. When you have the action to sling or release and you see the object picture in a hint (for sling), you should be able to perform the action.
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	-- Reaparicio --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	Si mors, pots reapareixer a la base, als dos UH-80 o a un company viu.
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	-- HALO --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	Pots fer un salt HALO al mapa d'Altis a la zona de reaparicio de base. Inicia HALO des del menu d'accions, i un cop al mapa, fes un sol clic esquerre on vulguis saltar. El mapa es tancara automaticament un moment després de fer clic. Si decideixes que no vols fer salt HALO, prem el boto ESCAPE del teclat, o la M per tancar el mapa i sortir del HALO. El paracaigudes s'obre automaticament una vegada que estiguis per sota del 60 metres d'altitud. Pots obrir manualment el paracaigudes a traves del menu d'accions.
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	-- Teletransport --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	Pots teletransportar-te entre zones fent servir els cartells de Teletransport.
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	-- Zeus --
	<br />
	-------------------
	<br />
	Els Instructors i Entrenadors tenen acces a Zeus.
